info.headline: IPAWS Message - MI Stay Home Stay Safe Extension 5/15
info.description: From the Governor's Office: The State of Michigan has extended the Stay Home Stay Safe order until May 15 to save lives. Individuals are strongly encouraged to wear a homemade, non-medical grade mask when they leave the house. Some restrictions have been lifted. For additional guidance, see www.michigan.gov/coronavirus
